Name: PROPHUNT™
About the game: Hide among the various props of the world, or find the imposters who are hiding among the props. Play as a hunter and flush out the players hidden in props or play as a prop who must hide from the hunters by morphing into objects. Hunter choose from four available classes adopt a different gameplay for each class: machine gun, assault rifle, heavy machine gun, shotgun, pistol or grenade launcher a flashlight for better visibility in dark areas Prop a dynamic rotation system to easily hide taunts to tease the hunters almost all objects in the maps are imitable to hide Features realistic graphics 2 game modes: simple and swap 4 maps with dynamic game elements: Warehouse, Bunker, Hangar and Police station host online games for up to 16 players secure your games with passwords or invite your friends directly via Steam join worldwide games via the server browser or quick game search
